name: KubeStellar
maturity: CNCF Sandbox
homepage: https://kubestellar.io/
documentation: https://kubestellar.io/docs/introduction
summary: KubeStellar is a Kubernetes-native multi-cluster orchestration platform that enables organizations to deploy and manage applications consistently across multiple Kubernetes clusters, cloud providers, and edge environments through a unified control plane.
facts:
  - Deploy applications across multiple Kubernetes clusters from a single control plane.
  - Continue using familiar Kubernetes APIs, tooling, and workflows.
sources:
